file.name: general.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: General Component
  version: 1.0.0

paths: {}

components:
  schemas:
    DisplayInfo:
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
        description:
          type: string
        language:
          type: string
        script:
          type: string
        region:
          type: string
        is_default:
          type: boolean
      required:
        - name
        - language
        - is_default
    Label:
      type: object
      properties:
        key:
          type: string
        value:
          type: string
      required:
        - key
        - value
